    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在冰封的荒漠中挖掘、战斗并生存——这是一场 Roguelike 冒险。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是 Froggy，一位坚定的幸存者，身处敌意重重的雪原。挖掘雪中的隧道，对抗诡异的生物，并在一个以温暖为生存之本的世界中适应下来——寒冷并不是唯一致命的威胁。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/749da7a5602ed09e4156518c7a3d4f91.poster.avif?t=1771541427\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/749da7a5602ed09e4156518c7a3d4f91.webm?t=1771541427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/749da7a5602ed09e4156518c7a3d4f91.mp4?t=1771541427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>生存循环</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险都从温暖安全的家中开始。接下来你将：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探险进入被雪覆盖的荒原</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用双手、铲子、火焰喷射器，甚至炸药来挖掘</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现散落的宝藏、陷阱和敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将资源带回家储存，不断变得更强</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/56d1d9ebdff68fd7784c2438080f0217.poster.avif?t=1771541427\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/56d1d9ebdff68fd7784c2438080f0217.webm?t=1771541427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/56d1d9ebdff68fd7784c2438080f0217.mp4?t=1771541427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>穿越冰封的荒原</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每张新地图都隐藏着独特的首领、危险与秘密。收集足够的钥匙来打开逃生之门，或者将它们用于宝箱以获得强力升级。明智地管理资源，是生存与失败之间的关键区别。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生存与 Roguelike 动作相结合</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一堆雪下都可能藏着宝藏、陷阱或潜伏的敌人。穿过可交互的积雪挖出隧道，在战斗中将其用作掩体，或引爆、融化它以揭开隐藏的秘密。若在寒冷中停留太久，你会被冻僵——除非你解锁了合适的升级！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/34a54cfffb7a0022e7ff731ffc6e9302.poster.avif?t=1771541427\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/34a54cfffb7a0022e7ff731ffc6e9302.webm?t=1771541427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/34a54cfffb7a0022e7ff731ffc6e9302.mp4?t=1771541427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级、适应并不断尝试</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用宝石在多条 Roguelite 技能路径上提升自己，打造独特的游戏风格：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为更快的挖掘者、更强的战士，或更能抵御严寒的生存者</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁铲子、火焰喷射器和炸药，探索全新的挖掘与战斗方式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用滑雪板在冰原上高速移动，把推车装满宝石以解锁更强大的力量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募企鹅、鼹鼠或猫头鹰等伙伴，在旅途中助你一臂之力</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>异常区域的风险与回报</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘的异常区域散布在冰封的荒原之中。进入其中意味着要面对致命的挑战——但若能生还，你将获得强大的宝物和稀有的神器。每件神器都会加入你的收藏，解锁未来冒险的新可能性。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>古怪又危险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前一刻，你还是穿着毛衣和围巾、悠然挖雪的青蛙。下一刻，你便在与诡异的黑暗奇幻风生物战斗。每个敌人都有独特的行为模式——掌握它们的弱点，才能生存下去。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >互动式积雪 —— 挖掘、打通隧道、重塑世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核心生存循环 —— 每次探险都要探索、收集并带回资源</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃脱或征服 —— 找到出口之门或击败最终 Boss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵活的 Roguelike 升级系统 —— 无数构筑与玩法风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存玩法 —— 在探索、战斗与严寒威胁之间保持平衡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊升级与伙伴 —— 解锁工具、武器与盟友</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种敌人与史诗级 Boss —— 掌握各自独特的行为模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决策与策略 —— 每次冒险都迫使你做出艰难选择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽的可重玩性 —— 每一局都有新的宝藏与危险</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/fc6fbf3bd01b6f937cad23c8480a146f.poster.avif?t=1771541427\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/fc6fbf3bd01b6f937cad23c8480a146f.webm?t=1771541427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232380/extras/fc6fbf3bd01b6f937cad23c8480a146f.mp4?t=1771541427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
